## Iterating in React

We're probably familiar with using `for loops` to iterate through lists in our Views

#### SomeView.html
```html
<ul>
  {% for book in books %}
    <li>{{ book.title }} ({{ book.author }})</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
```

But how should we do this in our React Components?

